om Bus Tour || Crazy Bus || || || || || || ||  || || 2011-<ref name=\"Official - Pleasure Beach Blackpool - Nickelodeon Land Map\"/> || ||\n|-\n| Blue Flyer || Junior Roller Coaster || || || || || || ||  ||  || [[Blue Flyer|2011-]]<ref name=\"Official - Pleasure Beach Blackpool - Nickelodeon Land Map\"/> || ||\n|- \n| Blue's Skidoo || Rotating Flat Ride ||  ||  ||  || 2003-2011<ref name=\"DW closure PR\" /><ref name=\"Official - Dreamworld - Park Map\"/> ||  || 2005\u20132009 || 2008-<ref name=MOA /> || 2007-2018<ref name=\"Official - Movie Park Germany\"/> ||  || 2019 ||\n|- \n| Boots Balloon Race || Balloon Ride ||  ||  || ????-2009 ||  ||  ||  ||  ||  ||  || || \n|-\n| BrainSurge || [[UniCoaster]] ||  ||  ||  ||  ||  ||  || [[BrainSurge (attraction)|2010-]] ||  || || || \n|-\n| Bubble Guppies Guppy Bubbler || Spinning Tower Ride ||  ||  ||  ||  ||  ||  || 2015-<ref name=MOA /> ||  ||  || || \n|- \n| Carousel || Carousel ||  ||  ||  ||  ||  ||  || 2008-<ref name=MOA /> ||  ||  || || \n|-\n| Crazy Cars || Bumper cars ||  ||  ||  ||  ||  ||  || 2008-<ref name=MOA /> ||  ||  || || \n|- \n| Danny Phantom Flyers || Kite Flyer ||  ||  ||  ||  ||  || 2006\u20132007 ||  ||  ||  || || \n|- \n| Danny Phantom Ghost Zone || Teacups ||  ||  ||  ||  ||  ||  ||  || 2007-<ref name=\"Official - Movie Park Germany\"/> ||  || || \n|-\n| Danny Phantom Ghost Zone || [[Ali Baba (ride)|Falling Star]] ||  ||  ||  ||  ||  ||  || [[Danny Phantom Ghost Zone|2008-2015]] ||  ||  || || \n|-\n| Diego's Rainforest Rescue || Balloon Ride || || || || || || || ||  || 2011-<ref name=\"Official - Pleasure Beach Blackpool - Nickelodeon Land Map\"/> || ||\n|- \n| Diego's Rescue Rider || Rotating Flat Ride ||  ||  ||  ||  ||  ||  ||  || 2007-<ref name=\"Official - Movie Park Germany\"/> || || \n|-\n| Diego's Rescue Rider || Crazy Bus ||  ||  ||  ||  ||  ||  || 2008-<ref name=MOA /> ||  || \n || ||\n|- \n| Dora's Adventure Express || Children's Train ||  ||  ||  ||  ||  ||  ||  || 2007-<ref name=\"Offici